{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you explore the shadowy halls, solve intricate puzzles that unlock the secrets of the corporate nightmare. But beware! Monstrous entities lurk around every corner, waiting to pounce on the unsuspecting. Communication and collaboration are key\u2014can you work together to escape the horrors that await?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Levels will be added throughout early access.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268130/extras/coop.png?t=1737118311\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore alone or  with a team up with 3 others\u00a0for a total of 4 player co-op. You\u00a0must find the exit alive to escape. Trapped in a nightmarish office environment, you and your friends must navigate through five uniquely terrifying levels, each brimming with suspense and mystery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268130/extras/1080p_23_Sub_09.gif?t=1737118311\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268130/extras/exp.png?t=1737118311\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With a haunting atmosphere and unpredictable gameplay, <i>Endless Shift</i> will keep you on the edge of your seat. Face your fears, unravel the dark truths, and discover who among you can endure the endless shift of terror. Are you ready to escape the nightmare?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268130/extras/5.gif?t=1737118311\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268130/extras/uniquelevels.png?t=1737118311\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Traverse though 5 unique levels with different puzzles and entities. Each level features a different way to escape with various puzzles along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268130/extras/657.gif?t=1737118311\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268130/extras/voicechat.png?t=1737118311\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The built-in voice chat adds even more tension and realism to the gameplay. Players can easily communicate with each other, discussing strategies, sharing discoveries, and warning about approaching entities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Warning</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game contains flashing lights that may make it unsuitable for people with photosensitive epilepsy or other photosensitive conditions. Player discretion is advised.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3268130?t=1737118311","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268130/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1737118311","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268130/3f1d930f1a88cb8e36a6028e29c4c396ef195e81/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737118311","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268130/3f1d930f1a88cb8e36a6028e29c4c396ef195e81/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737118311","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you explore the shadowy halls, solve intricate puzzles that unlock the secrets of the corporate nightmare. But beware! Monstrous entities lurk around every corner, waiting to pounce on the unsuspecting. Communication and collaboration are key\u2014can you work together to escape the horrors that await?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Levels will be added throughout early access.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268130/extras/coop.png?t=1737118311\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore alone or  with a team up with 3 others\u00a0for a total of 4 player co-op. You\u00a0must find the exit alive to escape. Trapped in a nightmarish office environment, you and your friends must navigate through five uniquely terrifying levels, each brimming with suspense and mystery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268130/extras/1080p_23_Sub_09.gif?t=1737118311\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268130/extras/exp.png?t=1737118311\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With a haunting atmosphere and unpredictable gameplay, <i>Endless Shift</i> will keep you on the edge of your seat. Face your fears, unravel the dark truths, and discover who among you can endure the endless shift of terror. Are you ready to escape the nightmare?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268130/extras/5.gif?t=1737118311\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268130/extras/uniquelevels.png?t=1737118311\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Traverse though 5 unique levels with different puzzles and entities. Each level features a different way to escape with various puzzles along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268130/extras/657.gif?t=1737118311\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268130/extras/voicechat.png?t=1737118311\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The built-in voice chat adds even more tension and realism to the gameplay. Players can easily communicate with each other, discussing strategies, sharing discoveries, and warning about approaching entities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Warning</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game contains flashing lights that may make it unsuitable for people with photosensitive epilepsy or other photosensitive conditions. Player discretion is advised.</p>","developers":["Ivan Huliakevich"],"genres":[{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3268130/header.jpg?t=1737118311","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257066617,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257066617/movie480.mp4?t=1729955745","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257066617/movie_max.mp4?t=1729955745"},"name":"Gameplay | Early Access","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257066617/286341b11befdbcb649ddb0438dda28ab7ebbb43/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1729955745","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257066617/movie48